{
  "module": "01-layout.md",
  "group": "01 — Layout & Container Components",
  "apiCount": 11,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "Column",
      "purpose": "沿垂直方向布局的容器",
      "anchor": "column",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Row",
      "purpose": "沿水平方向布局的容器",
      "anchor": "row",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Stack",
      "purpose": "堆叠容器，子组件依次入栈，后一个覆盖前一个",
      "anchor": "stack",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Flex",
      "purpose": "以弹性方式布局子组件的容器",
      "anchor": "flex",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "RelativeContainer",
      "purpose": "相对布局组件，用于复杂场景中元素对齐",
      "anchor": "relativecontainer",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Scroll",
      "purpose": "可滚动的容器组件，当子组件尺寸超过父组件时内容可滚动",
      "anchor": "scroll",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "List",
      "purpose": "列表容器，包含一系列相同宽度的列表项，支持懒加载",
      "anchor": "list",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Grid",
      "purpose": "网格容器，由行和列分割的单元格组成，支持跨行跨列",
      "anchor": "grid",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Blank",
      "purpose": "空白填充组件，在容器主轴方向上自动填充空余部分",
      "anchor": "blank",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Divider",
      "purpose": "分割线组件，分割不同内容块/内容元素",
      "anchor": "divider",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Badge",
      "purpose": "信息标记组件，附加在单个组件上用于信息提醒",
      "anchor": "badge",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "所有 ArkUI 布局/容器组件均为内置组件，无需显式 import。",
    "Scroll、List、Grid 等滚动组件不允许绑定同一个 Scroller 控制对象。",
    "Flex 组件存在二次布局过程，对性能有严格要求的场景建议使用 Column/Row 替代。",
    "List 推荐结合 LazyForEach 或带 virtualScroll 的 Repeat 使用，并设置 cachedCount 预加载。",
    "Grid 可通过 GridLayoutOptions 的 irregularIndexes 和 onGetIrregularSizeByIndex 实现不规则 GridItem 布局。",
    "Blank 仅在父组件为 Row/Column/Flex 时生效，且父组件需设置主轴方向大小。",
    "Badge 当 count 小于等于 0 时标记不显示；从 API 12 开始显隐支持 scale 动效。"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

{
  "module": "02-navigation.md",
  "group": "02 — Navigation & Tabs",
  "apiCount": 7,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "Tabs",
      "purpose": "页签式内容视图切换容器组件",
      "anchor": "tabs",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "TabContent",
      "purpose": "Tabs 的单个页签内容视图",
      "anchor": "tabcontent",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Navigation",
      "purpose": "路由导航根视图容器，支持 NavRouter 和 NavPathStack 两种模式",
      "anchor": "navigation",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "NavRouter",
      "purpose": "导航点击响应组件，API 13 起停止维护，推荐使用 NavPathStack",
      "anchor": "navrouter-deprecated",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "NavPathStack",
      "purpose": "导航栈控制器，管理 Navigation 中所有子页面的入栈出栈",
      "anchor": "navpathstack10",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.router (router.pushUrl)",
      "purpose": "页面路由 API，API 18 起废弃，推荐使用 Navigation 组件或 UIContext.getRouter()",
      "anchor": "ohos-router-页面路由不推荐",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "Router (UIContext.getRouter())",
      "purpose": "通过 UIContext 获取的 Router 实例，替代废弃的 @ohos.router API",
      "anchor": "class-router",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "Navigation + NavPathStack 是官方推荐的路由架构，@ohos.router(API 18废弃)和NavRouter(API 13废弃)均已被替代",
    "Tabs 仅支持 TabContent 作为直接子组件",
    "TabContent 宽度默认撑满 Tabs 父组件，高度由 Tabs 和 TabBar 决定",
    "TabBar 支持 SubTabBarStyle(文字+下划线) 和 BottomTabBarStyle(图标+文字) 两种样式",
    "NavPathStack pop 操作会缓存页面，后续 push 同名页面时优先复用",
    "Navigation 从 API 11 起默认支持安全区避让"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}

