      "purpose": "设备环境变量查询并存入AppStorage",
      "anchor": "environment",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@Env",
      "purpose": "组件级系统环境变量装饰器（V2，API 22+）",
      "anchor": "env",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "@State, @Prop, @Link 三个V1装饰器的正式API签名不在harmonyos-references中，存在于harmonyos-guides开发者指南",
    "@Consume @ObjectLink 同样缺失正式API签名，仅在错误码和示例中间接引用",
    "AppStorage旧版驼峰API(Link/SetAndLink/Prop等)从API 10起废弃，应使用小写新版",
    "Environment有两套方案: V1(envProp/envProps, API 10+)和V2(@Env装饰器, API 22+)",
    "@Env (V2) 使用SystemProperties枚举(BREAK_POINT/WINDOW_SIZE等)，Stage模型专用",
    "@Watch是唯一在本知识库中有完整签名定义的V1装饰器: Watch: (value: string) => PropertyDecorator"
  ],
  "missingApis": [
    "@State",
    "@Prop",
    "@Link",
    "@Consume",
    "@ObjectLink"
  ]
}

